# Ignition value proposition

## Key Value stories

- Guiding customers to find the right product offering for them
- Shortening sales cycle through lower-touch sales
- Reducing order errors

## Tagline ideation

Your turn-key solution to provide guided product discovery to your customers

Are you are a small company with a complicated set of product offerings?
Ignition is the tool that can transform your high touch sales process...


High touch sales through self service product discovery

Self service _ for complex products

Self service product configuration for complex offerings

Guided product discovery for customers


### Ideas

Creating catalogs:
...from a set of outfits
...from a set of rules
	- families are required
	- inclusions and exclusions are optional

### Content ideas

Content that triggers these thoughts in potential customers:
- "Yeah, I do spend a lot of time on that...Ignition would help!"
- "Yeah, I guess we do miss a lot of sales because of that...Ignition would help!"